<DATELINE>SOUTHAMPTON, N.Y. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   An 11-year-old was raped by her father
and 14-year-old brother and forced to watch her parents perform
sexual acts, police said.
   James and Eileen Robles, both 30, and their son were arrested
Friday night, said Southampton police Lt. Thomas Peyton.
   He said the girl had told friends of the family of the incidents,
and the friends called police. Investigators alleged that sometime
in September, and also on Thanksgiving Day, James Robles had sexual
intercourse with his daughter.
